<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<bpmn:definitions xmlns:bpmn="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:dc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:di="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:zeebe="http://camunda.org/schema/zeebe/1.0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:modeler="http://camunda.org/schema/modeler/1.0" id="Definitions_LoanDocumentIdp" targetNamespace="http://bpmn.io/schema/bpmn" exporter="Camunda Modeler" exporterVersion="5.49.0" modeler:executionPlatform="Camunda Cloud" modeler:executionPlatformVersion="8.8.0">
  <bpmn:process id="loan-document-idp-process" name="Loan Document IDP" isExecutable="true">
    <bpmn:startEvent id="start_event_document_uploaded" name="Document&#10;Uploaded">
      <bpmn:outgoing>flow_start_to_store</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:startEvent>
    <bpmn:serviceTask id="task_store_document" name="Store&#10;Document">
      <bpmn:documentation>Uploads the loan document at its local filesystem path (e.g. D:\Loan.pdf) into
Camunda 8's native Document Store via CamundaClient.newCreateDocumentCommand().
Camunda's own document store acts as the object storage — no custom
persistence layer is needed, and the reference is viewable/downloadable
directly from Operate and Tasklist.

Output variables:
  loanDocument     — Camunda document reference (DocumentReferenceResponse)
  documentStoredAt — epoch millis of storage</bpmn:documentation>
      <bpmn:extensionElements>
        <zeebe:taskDefinition type="idp.store-document" retries="3" />
      </bpmn:extensionElements>
      <bpmn:incoming>flow_start_to_store</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>flow_store_to_extract</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:serviceTask>
    <bpmn:serviceTask id="task_extract_document" name="Extract&#10;Document Data" zeebe:modelerTemplate="io.camunda:idp-unstructured-connector-template" zeebe:modelerTemplateVersion="1">
      <bpmn:documentation>Calls Camunda 8's native out-of-the-box IDP Unstructured Extraction
connector (job type io.camunda:idp-unstructured-connector-template:1, from the
"connectors" service in docker-compose-full.yaml) — real AI extraction, no custom
Java worker involved.

Extraction method: UNSTRUCTURED — Apache PDFBox pulls the raw text out of the stored
loanDocument locally (no AWS OCR needed, the PDF has real embedded text), then AWS
Bedrock (Amazon Nova, model amazon.nova-micro-v1:0, region us-east-1 — hardcoded since
Bedrock model availability is region-specific and differs from the general
IDP_AWS_REGION secret) reads that text and maps it onto the 4 taxonomy fields below
using each field's natural-language prompt. This is the right method for freeform
"Label: value" style documents; STRUCTURED/Textract Forms was tried first and returned
zero fields against this document, because Textract's Forms detector is a spatial/visual
form-field detector (boxed scanned forms), not a plain-text-paragraph parser.
Credentials are resolved from Connector secrets (see connector-secrets.txt):
IDP_AWS_ACCESSKEY, IDP_AWS_SECRETKEY.

Raw connector response (ExtractionResult) is captured as idpExtractionResult:
{
  "extractedFields": { "borrowerName": "John Smith", "propertyAddress": "...", ... },
  "metadata": { "tokenUsage": 123, "latencyMs": 842 }
}

Unstructured mode has no per-field confidence score, so resultExpression derives
confidence as (# of the 4 taxonomy fields that came back non-null) / 4, and reshapes
the rest into the extractedDataResponse the rest of the process expects. loanNumber is
deliberately NOT included here — it's already a top-level process variable (visible in
Operate/Tasklist on its own), and resultExpression's FEEL scope only ever exposes
"response" (the connector's own output), not other process variables, so trying to
smuggle loanNumber in here would just silently resolve to null:
{
  "borrowerName":    "John Smith",
  "propertyAddress": "123 Main Street, New York",
  "loanAmount":      350000,
  "closingDate":     "2026-08-15",
  "confidence":      1
}

Business Rule Task reads: extractedDataResponse.confidence</bpmn:documentation>
      <bpmn:extensionElements>
        <zeebe:taskDefinition type="io.camunda:idp-unstructured-connector-template:1" retries="3" />
        <zeebe:ioMapping>
          <zeebe:input source="=&#34;pdfBox&#34;" target="extractor.type" />
          <zeebe:input source="=&#34;bedrockAi&#34;" target="ai.type" />
          <zeebe:input source="=&#34;credentials&#34;" target="ai.awsAuthType" />
          <zeebe:input source="=&#34;{{secrets.IDP_AWS_ACCESSKEY}}&#34;" target="ai.accessKey" />
          <zeebe:input source="=&#34;{{secrets.IDP_AWS_SECRETKEY}}&#34;" target="ai.secretKey" />
          <zeebe:input source="=&#34;us-east-1&#34;" target="ai.region" />
          <zeebe:input source="=loanDocument" target="input.document" />
          <zeebe:input source="=[{name:&#34;borrowerName&#34;,prompt:&#34;The full legal name of the loan borrower&#34;},{name:&#34;propertyAddress&#34;,prompt:&#34;The property address associated with the loan&#34;},{name:&#34;loanAmount&#34;,prompt:&#34;The loan amount, as a plain number with no currency symbol or thousands separators&#34;},{name:&#34;closingDate&#34;,prompt:&#34;The closing date of the loan, in YYYY-MM-DD format&#34;}]" target="input.taxonomyItems" />
          <zeebe:input source="=&#34;amazon.nova-micro-v1:0&#34;" target="input.converseData.modelId" />
          <zeebe:input source="=1024" target="input.converseData.maxTokens" />
          <zeebe:input source="=0" target="input.converseData.temperature" />
        </zeebe:ioMapping>
        <zeebe:taskHeaders>
          <zeebe:header key="resultVariable" value="idpExtractionResult" />
          <zeebe:header key="resultExpression" value="={extractedDataResponse: {borrowerName: response.extractedFields.borrowerName, propertyAddress: response.extractedFields.propertyAddress, loanAmount: response.extractedFields.loanAmount, closingDate: response.extractedFields.closingDate, confidence: count([response.extractedFields.borrowerName, response.extractedFields.propertyAddress, response.extractedFields.loanAmount, response.extractedFields.closingDate][item != null]) / 4}}" />
        </zeebe:taskHeaders>
      </bpmn:extensionElements>
      <bpmn:incoming>flow_store_to_extract</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>flow_extract_to_evaluate</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:serviceTask>
    <bpmn:businessRuleTask id="task_evaluate_confidence" name="Evaluate&#10;Confidence">
      <bpmn:documentation>Zeebe DMN engine decision (idp-confidence-rules.dmn, hit policy FIRST) — no Java
worker needed. Reads extractedDataResponse.confidence and decides whether the
loan officer must review the extracted data before registration.

reviewRequired = true  → confidence &lt; 0.9 (human review required)
reviewRequired = false → confidence &gt;= 0.9 (auto-register)</bpmn:documentation>
      <bpmn:extensionElements>
        <zeebe:calledDecision decisionId="idp-confidence-rules" resultVariable="reviewRequired" />
      </bpmn:extensionElements>
      <bpmn:incoming>flow_extract_to_evaluate</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>flow_evaluate_to_gw_confidence</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:businessRuleTask>
    <bpmn:exclusiveGateway id="gw_confidence_ok" name="Review&#10;Required?">
      <bpmn:incoming>flow_evaluate_to_gw_confidence</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>flow_gw_confidence_to_register</bpmn:outgoing>
      <bpmn:outgoing>flow_gw_confidence_to_review</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:exclusiveGateway>
    <bpmn:userTask id="task_review_extracted_data" name="Review&#10;Extracted Data">
      <bpmn:extensionElements>
        <zeebe:assignmentDefinition assignee="loan-officer" />
        <zeebe:userTask />
      </bpmn:extensionElements>
      <bpmn:incoming>flow_gw_confidence_to_review</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>flow_review_to_register</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:userTask>
    <bpmn:serviceTask id="task_register_loan" name="Register&#10;Loan">
      <bpmn:documentation>Registers the loan using the (possibly human-corrected) extracted document
data. Simulates the downstream POST /loan/register business API call.

Output variables:
  loanId         — generated loan registration reference
  loanRegistered — true
  registeredAt   — epoch millis of registration</bpmn:documentation>
      <bpmn:extensionElements>
        <zeebe:taskDefinition type="idp.register-loan" retries="3" />
      </bpmn:extensionElements>
      <bpmn:incoming>flow_gw_confidence_to_register</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:incoming>flow_review_to_register</bpmn:incoming>
      <bpmn:outgoing>flow_register_to_end</bpmn:outgoing>
    </bpmn:serviceTask>
    <bpmn:endEvent id="end_loan_registered" name="Loan&#10;Registered">
      <bpmn:incoming>flow_register_to_end</bpmn:incoming>
    </bpmn:endEvent>
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="flow_start_to_store" sourceRef="start_event_document_uploaded" targetRef="task_store_document" />
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="flow_store_to_extract" sourceRef="task_store_document" targetRef="task_extract_document" />
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="flow_extract_to_evaluate" sourceRef="task_extract_document" targetRef="task_evaluate_confidence" />
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="flow_evaluate_to_gw_confidence" sourceRef="task_evaluate_confidence" targetRef="gw_confidence_ok" />
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="flow_gw_confidence_to_register" name="No" sourceRef="gw_confidence_ok" targetRef="task_register_loan">
      <bpmn:conditionExpression xsi:type="bpmn:tFormalExpression">=reviewRequired = false</bpmn:conditionExpression>
    </bpmn:sequenceFlow>
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="flow_gw_confidence_to_review" name="Yes" sourceRef="gw_confidence_ok" targetRef="task_review_extracted_data">
      <bpmn:conditionExpression xsi:type="bpmn:tFormalExpression">=reviewRequired = true</bpmn:conditionExpression>
    </bpmn:sequenceFlow>
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="flow_review_to_register" sourceRef="task_review_extracted_data" targetRef="task_register_loan" />
    <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="flow_register_to_end" sourceRef="task_register_loan" targetRef="end_loan_registered" />
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="TextAnnotation_storeDocumentIo">
      <bpmn:text>// task_store_document — I/O mapping
{
  "input": {
    "documentId":   "string (process variable)",
    "documentPath": "string — local filesystem path, e.g. D:\\Loan.pdf"
  },
  "output": {
    "loanDocument":     "DocumentReferenceResponse (Zeebe document-ref variable)",
    "documentStoredAt": "long (epoch millis)"
  }
}</bpmn:text>
    </bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="TextAnnotation_extractDocumentIo">
      <bpmn:text>// task_extract_document — io.camunda:idp-unstructured-connector-template:1
{
  "input (zeebe:input)": {
    "extractor.type":    "\"pdfBox\" (local text extraction, no S3/Textract needed)",
    "ai.type":            "\"bedrockAi\"",
    "ai.awsAuthType":     "\"credentials\"",
    "ai.accessKey":       "{{secrets.IDP_AWS_ACCESSKEY}}",
    "ai.secretKey":       "{{secrets.IDP_AWS_SECRETKEY}}",
    "ai.region":          "\"us-east-1\" (hardcoded — Bedrock model availability is region-specific)",
    "input.document":     "loanDocument (from task_store_document)",
    "input.taxonomyItems": "[{name, prompt}, ...] — one per extracted field",
    "input.converseData.modelId": "\"amazon.nova-micro-v1:0\""
  },
  "output (zeebe:taskHeaders resultVariable + resultExpression)": {
    "idpExtractionResult": "raw ExtractionResult { extractedFields, metadata } (resultVariable)",
    "extractedDataResponse": {
      "borrowerName":    "string (from response.extractedFields — resultExpression scope is response-only)",
      "propertyAddress": "string",
      "loanAmount":      "number",
      "closingDate":     "string",
      "confidence":      "double 0-1 (# of 4 taxonomy fields extracted non-null / 4)"
    }
  },
  "loanNumber": "NOT nested in extractedDataResponse on purpose — resultExpression can't see process variables, and it's already visible on its own as a top-level process variable"
}</bpmn:text>
    </bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="TextAnnotation_evaluateConfidenceIo">
      <bpmn:text>// task_evaluate_confidence — I/O mapping (DMN: idp-confidence-rules)
{
  "input": {
    "extractedDataResponse.confidence": "double"
  },
  "output": {
    "reviewRequired": "boolean"
  }
}</bpmn:text>
    </bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="TextAnnotation_registerLoanIo">
      <bpmn:text>// task_register_loan — I/O mapping
{
  "input": {
    "documentId":            "string (process variable)",
    "extractedDataResponse": "object (possibly human-corrected via task_review_extracted_data)"
  },
  "output": {
    "loanId":         "string",
    "loanRegistered": "boolean",
    "registeredAt":   "long"
  }
}</bpmn:text>
    </bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:association id="assoc_store_document_io" sourceRef="task_store_document" targetRef="TextAnnotation_storeDocumentIo" />
    <bpmn:association id="assoc_extract_document_io" sourceRef="task_extract_document" targetRef="TextAnnotation_extractDocumentIo" />
    <bpmn:association id="assoc_evaluate_confidence_io" sourceRef="task_evaluate_confidence" targetRef="TextAnnotation_evaluateConfidenceIo" />
    <bpmn:association id="assoc_register_loan_io" sourceRef="task_register_loan" targetRef="TextAnnotation_registerLoanIo" />
  </bpmn:process>
  <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="BPMNDiagram_1">
    <bpmndi:BPMNPlane id="BPMNPlane_1" bpmnElement="loan-document-idp-process">
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="start_event_document_uploaded_di" bpmnElement="start_event_document_uploaded">
        <dc:Bounds x="690" y="1052" width="36" height="36" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
          <dc:Bounds x="683" y="1095" width="51" height="27" />
        </bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="task_store_document_di" bpmnElement="task_store_document">
        <dc:Bounds x="780" y="1030" width="110" height="80" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="task_extract_document_di" bpmnElement="task_extract_document">
        <dc:Bounds x="940" y="1030" width="110" height="80" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="task_evaluate_confidence_di" bpmnElement="task_evaluate_confidence">
        <dc:Bounds x="1100" y="1030" width="110" height="80" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="gw_confidence_ok_di" bpmnElement="gw_confidence_ok" isMarkerVisible="true">
        <dc:Bounds x="1270" y="1045" width="50" height="50" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
          <dc:Bounds x="1270" y="1102" width="51" height="27" />
        </bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="task_review_extracted_data_di" bpmnElement="task_review_extracted_data">
        <dc:Bounds x="1390" y="1190" width="110" height="80" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="task_register_loan_di" bpmnElement="task_register_loan">
        <dc:Bounds x="1520" y="1030" width="110" height="80" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="end_loan_registered_di" bpmnElement="end_loan_registered">
        <dc:Bounds x="1690" y="1052" width="36" height="36" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
          <dc:Bounds x="1682" y="1095" width="54" height="27" />
        </bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="assoc_store_document_io_di" bpmnElement="assoc_store_document_io">
        <di:waypoint x="788" y="1031" />
        <di:waypoint x="430" y="752" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="assoc_extract_document_io_di" bpmnElement="assoc_extract_document_io">
        <di:waypoint x="965" y="1030" />
        <di:waypoint x="831" y="637" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="TextAnnotation_evaluateConfidenceIo_di" bpmnElement="TextAnnotation_evaluateConfidenceIo">
        <dc:Bounds x="1110" y="723" width="250" height="172" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="TextAnnotation_registerLoanIo_di" bpmnElement="TextAnnotation_registerLoanIo">
        <dc:Bounds x="1530" y="694" width="260" height="230" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="flow_start_to_store_di" bpmnElement="flow_start_to_store">
        <di:waypoint x="726" y="1070" />
        <di:waypoint x="780" y="1070" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="flow_store_to_extract_di" bpmnElement="flow_store_to_extract">
        <di:waypoint x="890" y="1070" />
        <di:waypoint x="940" y="1070" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="flow_extract_to_evaluate_di" bpmnElement="flow_extract_to_evaluate">
        <di:waypoint x="1050" y="1070" />
        <di:waypoint x="1100" y="1070" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="flow_evaluate_to_gw_confidence_di" bpmnElement="flow_evaluate_to_gw_confidence">
        <di:waypoint x="1210" y="1070" />
        <di:waypoint x="1270" y="1070" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="flow_gw_confidence_to_register_di" bpmnElement="flow_gw_confidence_to_register">
        <di:waypoint x="1320" y="1070" />
        <di:waypoint x="1520" y="1070" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
          <dc:Bounds x="1411" y="1052" width="15" height="14" />
        </bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="flow_gw_confidence_to_review_di" bpmnElement="flow_gw_confidence_to_review">
        <di:waypoint x="1295" y="1095" />
        <di:waypoint x="1295" y="1230" />
        <di:waypoint x="1390" y="1230" />
        <bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
          <dc:Bounds x="1302" y="1150" width="18" height="14" />
        </bpmndi:BPMNLabel>
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="flow_review_to_register_di" bpmnElement="flow_review_to_register">
        <di:waypoint x="1500" y="1230" />
        <di:waypoint x="1575" y="1230" />
        <di:waypoint x="1575" y="1110" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="flow_register_to_end_di" bpmnElement="flow_register_to_end">
        <di:waypoint x="1630" y="1070" />
        <di:waypoint x="1690" y="1070" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="assoc_evaluate_confidence_io_di" bpmnElement="assoc_evaluate_confidence_io">
        <di:waypoint x="1174" y="1030" />
        <di:waypoint x="1207" y="895" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNEdge id="assoc_register_loan_io_di" bpmnElement="assoc_register_loan_io">
        <di:waypoint x="1578" y="1030" />
        <di:waypoint x="1612" y="924" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="TextAnnotation_storeDocumentIo_di" bpmnElement="TextAnnotation_storeDocumentIo">
        <dc:Bounds x="160" y="560" width="270" height="201" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="TextAnnotation_extractDocumentIo_di" bpmnElement="TextAnnotation_extractDocumentIo">
        <dc:Bounds x="550" y="80" width="281" height="633" />
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
    </bpmndi:BPMNPlane>
  </bpmndi:BPMNDiagram>
</bpmn:definitions>